I’m using SchoolMaker’s community as a selling point for my online courses. And it’s working !

![Image 113](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/61096a073266c13f17e3866e/611cbd8d8f29a82baf17223a_Cedric.avif)

I sent a survey to my students after switching to SchoolMaker. And **88.9% rated it as “very good”**.

![Image 114](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/61096a073266c13f17e3866e/67ea67973c041d5c87d335ab_diet%402x.avif)

Your customer support is just incredible -\> you should use that in your marketing campaigns !

![Image 115: Logo Ethique et Authentique](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/61096a073266c13f17e3866e/67601a669ffcdf42b700424e_454041081_1227265288596659_852617660918191692_n.avif)

What we really see is how it helps students move forward much faster, much further... We've had incredible rates of engagement and progress in the program.

![Image 116](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/61096a073266c13f17e3866e/67ea6beeb10aea7828377311_melina-dupont-opal.avif)

I've just recommended SchoolMaker to 2 different clients because I think it really fits the course structure we've created together.

![Image 117](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/61096a073266c13f17e3866e/67ea6c3ac50064165032ff91_sebastien%20vaquier%20seo.webp)

So far, support has been impeccable. Customer needs are taken into account to the point of perfection.Thank you!
